{"tid":1154091,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先爭啲死T.T","createTime":"2019-05-14T05:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T13:35:06.000Z","uid":431,"like":16,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"43b606ce77b67141024b7cfb5657a27bc30c9d2b","tid":1154091,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"搭搭下車無端端有浸爆屎渠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我戴住口罩 成浸味喺入邊long long下直頭食緊屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為點解自己個口咁撚臭直到望到其他人都臭到面容扭曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勁想大叫好撚臭啊！！！<br />\n你老尾應該整條喉連住自己個屎忽同個鼻一放屁自己食返晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺公眾場所放屁逼人硬食真係勁缺德屌你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defdfb3aace3935a56e14270063ac4af3ed4ad31","tid":1154091,"uid":36435,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"坐私家車"},{"pid":"6175e4e6fd4aecb0227555c2c7d77a3ef0070b2d","tid":1154091,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"defdfb3aace3935a56e14270063ac4af3ed4ad31","tid":1154091,"uid":36435,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"坐私家車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"好嬲啊我家陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044f22bf6f18eb794c9df488264c857626a440df","tid":1154091,"uid":36435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6175e4e6fd4aecb0227555c2c7d77a3ef0070b2d","tid":1154091,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"defdfb3aace3935a56e14270063ac4af3ed4ad31","tid":1154091,"uid":36435,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"坐私家車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:11:53.00